citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 10:50 AM on 5 Aug
21.
Inspectors tried to contact registrant/licensee at two phone numbers. Honked horn and spoke with employees, but the
registrant/licensee were not able to be contacted and did not return the call or arrive within 30 minutes.
Additional Inspectors:
William Campbell, VETERINARY MEDICAL OFFICEREnd Section
